o mesenchymal transition through a SMAD-independent signaling pathway through PARD6A phosphorylation and activation. {ECO:0000269|PubMed:15761148, ECO:0000269|PubMed:16754747, ECO:0000269|PubMed:18758450, ECO:0000269|PubMed:7774578, ECO:0000269|PubMed:8752209, ECO:0000269|PubMed:8980228, ECO:0000269|PubMed:9346908}.', 'Extracellular.{ECO:0000255}., Cytoplasmic.{ECO:0000255}.', 'length(34,126) = 93, length(148,503) = 356', 'Cell membrane {ECO:0000269|PubMed:9472030}; Single-pass type I membrane protein {ECO:0000269|PubMed:9472030}. Cell junction, tight junction {ECO:0000269|PubMed:15761148}.', '503 AA', '01-06-1994', '17-02-2016', '>sp|P36897|TGFR1_HUMAN\nMEAAVAAPRPRLLLLVLAAAAAAAAALLPGATALQCFCHLCTKDNFTCVTDGLCFVSVTE\nTTDKVIHNSMCIAEIDLIPRDRPFVCAPSSKTGSVTTTYCCNQDHCNKIELPTTVKSSPG\nLGPVELAAVIAGPVCFVCISLMLMVYICHNRTVIHHRVPNEEDPSLDRPFISEGTTLKDL\nIYDMTTSGSGSGLPLLVQRTIARTIVLQESIGKGRFGEVWRGKWRGEEVAVKIFSSREER\nSWFREAEIYQTVMLRHENILGFIAADNKDNGTWTQLWLVSDYHEHGSLFDYLNRYTVTVE\nGMIKLALSTASGLAHLHMEIVGTQGKPAIAHRDLKSKNILVKKNGTCCIADLGLAVRHDS\nATDTIDIAPNHRVGTKRYMAPEVLDDSINMKHFESFKRADIYAMGLVFWEIARRCSIGGI\nHEDYQLPYYDLVPSDPSVEEMRKVVCEQKLRPNIPNRWQSCEALRVMAKIMRECWYANGA\nARLTALRIKKTLSQLSQQEGIKM', 'Evidence at protein level', 1),
